name: LaptopSpecialist.com
overview:
A Nationwide Directory of Laptop Repair Shops, Technicians, Companies and Centers.

LaptopSpecialist.com a web portal in which Laptop Computer owners in the United States are referred to laptop Repair Specialist, Technicians and repair centers who pay fees for listing and /or leads. Repair shope, centers, companies and technicians are pre-screened for A+ certificate, licenses and experience as well as other related issues. There is no charge for laptop computer owners to use the service. Member contractors are charged fees for lisitng and/or per lead referral, depending on the type of job. The site also includes articles, features, marketplace and other related topics.
